query:
SELECT u.id as userId, u.name, u.email, a.id as accountId, a.storeName, a.marketplace
FROM users u
LEFT JOIN ad_accounts a ON u.id = a.userId
WHERE u.email = 'mcoceanyet@gmail.com';
